German Chancellor Merkel Says Leaders Will Not Let Euro Fail

-- B y   S i m o n e   M e i e r   a n d   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-10-19T15:50:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/german-chancellor-merkel-says-leaders-will-not-let-euro-fail.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel  said
she will not let the euro fail.  “If the euro fails,  Europe  fails. But we shall not allow
this to happen,” she said at an event in  Frankfurt  today.
“ Germany ’s fate is linked to the fate of Europe.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
